I remember is a motorbike by J.R. Thomas, they kept a - a grocers shop where Norton's the fish shop is now and - I think he's the first to have a motorbike. But I remember the first - aeroplane. I think it was - called Wright, traveling from - Penzance to
 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, a sort of competition, and he came down in a field and - outside Camborne, just outside. But he got away again next day I think.
