\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9067939\charrsid8926906 dropped}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11556911\charrsid8926906 
 my stick and started playing again. And then - when I got out my stick was gone. So I thought I had to go 
